nodes.text: Darth Vader 17 is the upcoming seventeenth issue of the 2020 comic book series Star Wars: Darth Vader, and is part of the Star Wars: War of the Bounty Hunters event. The issue will be written by Greg Pak, illustrated by Raffaele Ienco, and published by Marvel Comics on October 20, 2021.
